{"tid":1634383,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我正式宣布係冇交通前提下再叫人集中去港島遊行既就係鬼","createTime":"2019-10-07T07:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T10:51:21.000Z","uid":292024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"46244d9477d36c2c3cf7d3ce4cda8330c00ebbec","tid":1634383,"uid":292024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:45:24.000Z","msg":"眾所週知，港島區係送頭最嚴重既地方，每次大家都唔知食左乜藥係都要玩陣地戰，導致大量前線送頭，亦都唔排除有鬼要人打陣地拖時間俾班狗佈防<br />\n<br />\n1.住新界既必須過海難以撤離，隧道巴士會俾狗圍捕<br />\n2.遊行路線全部都係海旁，簡直就係死路，狗從內至外就輕易包抄<br />\n3.狗總係灣仔，大量狗可以玩大圍捕，再配合九龍班狗過海只有10分鐘<br />\n4.商業區唔似得周圍有屋邨私人地方俾大家入走避<br />\n5.家長過海接送困難倍增<br />\n<br />\n希望大家清楚時勢，而家已經唔係開頭黨鐵會開車車手足走嗰時，係而家大家冇交通情況下，搞集會請分開港島同新界<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家請珍惜前線手足，拉一個少一個</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">記住我地係橡根，政府係M巾</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">進又得退又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"091400a94c62d2703d6ecce9a698d82d1e641569","tid":1634383,"uid":105691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:51:21.000Z","msg":"認真推"}]}